# Archive Folder

This folder contains your published content archive.

## How to Use

Store your published content here:
- Published newsletters
- Published blog posts
- Published social media content
- Case studies
- Past campaigns

Claude references this to:
- Maintain consistency with past content
- Repurpose existing content
- Avoid repeating the same ideas
- Learn your voice from real examples

## Organization Tips

Create subfolders by content type:
- /newsletters - Past newsletter issues
- /blog-posts - Published articles
- /social - Social media content
- /emails - Past email campaigns

## Adding Content

The more content you add here, the better Claude understands your voice and can create consistent new content.
